"Install AISBench on the first host, which is the node with\n"
"`LWS_WORKER_INDEX=0`:"
msgstr "在第一个主机（即 `LWS_WORKER_INDEX=0` 的节点）上安装 AISBench："

msgid ""
"If your local image already contains the model, benchmark data, Ascend runtime,\n"
"and AISBench, you only need the run-time exports in the next step."
msgstr "如果你的本地镜像已经包含了模型、基准数据、Ascend 运行时和 AISBench，你只需要下一步中的运行时导出。"

msgid "##### 2.1.3 Start each node"
msgstr "##### 2.1.3 启动每个节点"

msgid ""
"Run the script on each node separately. Start worker nodes first, then start\n"
"node 0."
msgstr "在每个节点上分别运行脚本。先启动工作节点，然后启动节点 0。"

msgid "On node 1:"
msgstr "在节点 1 上："

msgid "On node 0:"
msgstr "在节点 0 上："

