"Internal DP logs are mainly printed to the terminal running `run.sh`. When\n"
"`LOG_PREFIX` is set, the shared script also backs up Ascend logs to:"
msgstr ""
"内部 DP 日志主要打印到运行 `run.sh` 的终端。当设置了 `LOG_PREFIX` 时，共享脚本还会将 Ascend 日志备份到："

msgid "#### 2.2 External DP local run"
msgstr "#### 2.2 外部 DP 本地运行"

msgid "##### 2.2.1 Add cluster hosts"
msgstr "##### 2.2.1 添加集群主机"

msgid "Edit the external DP config you want to run. For example:"
msgstr "编辑你想要运行的外部 DP 配置。例如："

msgid "##### 2.2.2 Prepare the environment"
msgstr "##### 2.2.2 准备环境"

msgid "Install AISBench on node 0:"
msgstr "在节点 0 上安装 AISBench："

msgid "##### 2.2.3 Start each node"
msgstr "##### 2.2.3 启动每个节点"

msgid ""
"External DP uses the same shared `run.sh`. Set `CONFIG_BASE_PATH` to the\n"
"external DP config directory so the script chooses\n"
"`external_dp/scripts/test_external_dp.py`."
msgstr ""
"外部 DP 使用相同的共享 `run.sh`。将 `CONFIG_BASE_PATH` 设置为外部 DP 配置目录，以便脚本选择 "
"`external_dp/scripts/test_external_dp.py`。"

msgid ""
"Then start non-master nodes first, and start node 0 last. The following example\n"
"uses `GLM5_1-W8A8-EP-external.yaml`, which is a 4-node disaggregated prefill\n"
"case."
msgstr ""
"然后先启动非主节点，最后启动节点 0。以下示例使用 `GLM5_1-W8A8-EP-external.yaml`，这是一个 4 节点分离式预填充案例。"

msgid "On node 1, node 2, and node 3, set the matching `LWS_WORKER_INDEX`:"
msgstr "在节点 1、节点 2 和节点 3 上，设置匹配的 `LWS_WORKER_INDEX`："

msgid ""
"For `GLM5_1-W8A8-EP-external.yaml`, node 0 and node 1 start prefiller ranks,\n"
"node 2 and node 3 start decoder ranks, and node 0 also starts the proxy and\n"
