msgstr ""
"运行 `run.sh` 的终端会打印 pytest 编排日志。对于外部 DP，AISBench 输出也会打印在节点 0 上，而 rank 和代理的 "
"stdout/stderr 则写入 `EXTERNAL_DP_LOG_DIR`。默认布局为："

msgid ""
"The first line of each rank log records the exact command and environment used\n"
"to start that rank. `proxy.log` exists only on the configured proxy node,\n"
"usually node 0."
msgstr ""
"每个 rank 日志的第一行记录了用于启动该 rank 的确切命令和环境。`proxy.log` 仅存在于配置的代理节点上，通常是节点 0。"

msgid "Use a separate log directory when running multiple local experiments:"
msgstr "在运行多个本地实验时，使用单独的日志目录："

msgid ""
"To watch logs in real time, run these commands in another terminal on the\n"
"corresponding node:"
msgstr "要实时查看日志，请在相应节点上的另一个终端中运行以下命令："
